{
  "stem": "24163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's really the second time that I re-entered this rotten country during the last few days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we're here to stay now, and God knows when I'll ever see France again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can tell by my news-- by the newscasts that we made quite a bit of progress along the Western Front during the last few weeks and crossed the Rhine in many places.' Which we did.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got across on a pontoon bridge. 'I've been with the Army for some time now and have been through cities all through Alsace and Lorraine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I then traveled through the Maginot Line and the impregnable, quote, unquote, 'secret line.' Both are mightily strong, heavily fortified defense lines.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But our dough boys and tanks crashed them just the same.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, now I am back in Germany sitting in a little room overlooking mountains and woods and the suburbs of a beautiful German city--' which I couldn't name, but I can tell you now what it is.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called Naishtat on the Rhine Schlosser.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Near what large city?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in southern Germany somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very beautiful area, OK? 'This city did not take too much of a beating by our Air Force, artillery, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we live in a big three-story house which belonged to a German industrialist, an ardent Nazi who fled with the retreating German troops.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Several Russian slave laborers greeted us with bottles of wine upon our arrival and seem to have done an excellent job of smashing everything in their former boss's house.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just ruined it inside.' They had cut the oriental carpetings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had cut the, the paintings on the wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
